  2. Description of Service                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                     
 ModaMatch is a fashion discovery application that provides:                                                                         
                                                                                                                                     
 - Visual Search: Upload screenshots or photos to find similar fashion items                                                     
 - Collections: Save and organize fashion items you discover                                                                     
 - Price Tracking: Monitor price changes on saved items                                                                          
 - Collection Sharing: Share your curated collections with others                                                                
                                                                                                                                     
  Service Availability                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                     
 We strive to provide reliable service, but ModaMatch is provided "as is" without guarantees of:                                     
 - Continuous availability                                                                                                           
 - Error-free operation                                                                                                              
 - Accuracy of search results or pricing information                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                     
